 XT : A bundle of tools for program transformation

 Version @VERSION@

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 Author: Eelco Visser <visser@acm.org>

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
 This package bundles a collection of independent tools that help in creating
 various components of program transformation systems. The contribution of this
 package is the bundle configuration, not the individual components. The tools 
 in this bundle are:

 - aterm	: a library for the representation of terms
 - gb 		: grammar base, a collection of SDF2 syntax definitions
 - gt		: grammar tools, a collection of tools for grammar engineering
 - sglr		: the scannerless, generalized-LR parser
 - stratego	: a language for specification of program transformation 
                  systems

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 INSTALLATION

 1) configure the package

	./configure --prefix=`pwd`

 2) make and install

	make install

